title: Generic UPS Device: Battery state
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/power/generic
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This checks monitors the following battery conditions, if available:
 "UPS is on battery",
 "Battery fault",
 "Battery to be replaced",
 "Low Battery",
 "Battery is not charging",
 "Battery is at low condition",
 "UPS is on bypass",
 "UPS is on battery backup time",
 "Overload"

 If one of them becomes active, the check will yield
 a critical state alongside the reason(s) as check summary.

inventory:
 One service is created for each UPS.
